<h1 id="åŠ›å­¦å¹³è¡¡ãªç£æ°—æµä½“å›è»¢ãƒˆãƒ¼ãƒ©ã‚¹">åŠ›å­¦å¹³è¡¡ãªç£æ°—æµä½“å›è»¢ãƒˆãƒ¼ãƒ©ã‚¹</h1>

<p>ã‚³ãƒ³ãƒ”ãƒ¥ãƒ¼ã‚¿ã®æ€§èƒ½ãŒå¤§å¹…ã«å‘ä¸Šã—ã€è¿‘å¹´ã§ã¯é™ç€å††ç›¤ã®ç£æ°—æµä½“è¨ˆç®—ãŒæ´»ç™ºã«è¡Œã‚ã‚Œã‚‹ã‚ˆã†ã«ãªã‚Šã¾ã—ãŸã€‚ã¾ãŸæœ€è¿‘ã§ã¯M87ã«å¼•ãç¶šãã€ç§ãŸã¡ãŒã„ã‚‹å¤©ã®å·éŠ€æ²³ã®ä¸­å¿ƒã«å­˜åœ¨ã™ã‚‹SMBH(Super Massive Black Hole; è¶…å·¨å¤§è³ªé‡ãƒ–ãƒ©ãƒƒã‚¯ãƒ›ãƒ¼ãƒ«)ãŒç›´æ¥æ’®åƒã•ã‚ŒãŸè¦³æ¸¬çµæœãŒç™»å ´ã™ã‚‹ãªã©ã€ã“ã®åˆ†é‡ãŒç››ã‚Šä¸ŠãŒã‚Šã‚’è¦‹ã›ã¦ã„ã¾ã™ã€‚ã“ã“ã§ã¯é™ç€å††ç›¤ã‚·ãƒŸãƒ¥ãƒ¬ãƒ¼ã‚·ãƒ§ãƒ³ã®åˆæœŸæ¡ä»¶ã¨ã—ã¦ç”¨ã„ã‚‰ã‚Œã‚‹ã€ç£æ°—æµä½“å›è»¢ãƒˆãƒ¼ãƒ©ã‚¹ã®å¼ã‚’å°å‡ºã—ã¾ã™ã€‚</p>

<h2 id="varphiæ–¹å‘ç£å ´ã‚’æŒã¤å ´åˆ">\(\varphi\)æ–¹å‘ç£å ´ã‚’æŒã¤å ´åˆ</h2>

<p>ã“ã“ã§ã¯å††å½¢ç£å ´ãŒè²«ã„ã¦ã„ã‚‹å›è»¢ãƒˆãƒ¼ãƒ©ã‚¹ã‚’è€ƒãˆã¾ã—ã‚‡ã†ã€‚ãªãŠã€å¤–å ´ã¨ã—ã¦ä¸ãˆã‚‰ã‚Œã¦ã„ã‚‹é‡åŠ›ãƒãƒ†ãƒ³ã‚·ãƒ£ãƒ«ã¯è»¸å¯¾ç§°ã§ã€\(\Phi (R, z)\)ã§ä¸ãˆã‚‰ã‚Œã‚‹ã¨ã—ã¾ã™ã€‚ã“ã®ãƒˆãƒ¼ãƒ©ã‚¹ã¯åŠ›å­¦å¹³è¡¡ã«ã‚ã‚‹ã¨è€ƒãˆã¦</p>

\[(é å¿ƒåŠ›) 
= (ãƒãƒ†ãƒ³ã‚·ãƒ£ãƒ«ã®å‹¾é…ã«ã‚ˆã‚‹åŠ›) + (åœ§åŠ›å‹¾é…ã«ã‚ˆã‚‹åŠ›) + (ç£æ°—å¼µåŠ›)\]

<p>ãŒæˆã‚Šç«‹ã£ã¦ã„ã‚‹ã¨ã—ã¾ã™ã€‚ã¾ãŸã€ãƒˆãƒ¼ãƒ©ã‚¹ã‚’æ§‹æˆã—ã¦ã„ã‚‹ã‚¬ã‚¹ã®å˜ä½è³ªé‡ã‚ãŸã‚Šã®è§’é‹å‹•é‡\(L_z\)ãŒ</p>

\[L_z 
= R v_\varphi 
= \ell_z \left( \frac{R}{R_b}\right)^a \tag{1}\]

<p>ã®ã‚ˆã†ã«ã€å›è»¢è»¸ã‹ã‚‰ã®è·é›¢\(R\)ã«ä¾å­˜ã™ã‚‹å½¢ã‚’è€ƒãˆã¾ã™ã€‚ã“ã“ã§\(R_b\)ã¯ãƒˆãƒ¼ãƒ©ã‚¹ã«ãŠã„ã¦ä¸€ç•ªå¯†åº¦ãŒå¤§ãããªã‚‹(ãƒˆãƒ¼ãƒ©ã‚¹ã®æœ€æ·±éƒ¨ã®)åº§æ¨™ã§ã‚ã‚Šã€\(L_z(R_b) = \ell_z\)ã¯ãƒˆãƒ¼ãƒ©ã‚¹æœ€æ·±éƒ¨ã®å˜ä½ä½“ç©ã‚ãŸã‚Šã®è§’é‹å‹•é‡ã§ã™ã€‚</p>

<h3 id="é‡£ã‚Šåˆã„ã®å¼">é‡£ã‚Šåˆã„ã®å¼</h3>

<p>ã¾ãšã¯\(R\)æ–¹å‘ã®é‡£ã‚Šåˆã„ã®å¼ã‹ã‚‰ã§ã™ã€‚å††å½¢ç£å ´ã‚’ä»®å®šã—ã¦ã„ã‚‹ãŸã‚ã€<a href="/mhd/momentum">ç£æ°—å¼µåŠ›</a>ã¯ç°¡å˜ãªå½¢ã¨ãªã‚‹ã“ã¨ã‚’åˆ©ç”¨ã—ã¦</p>

\[\frac{L_z^2}{R^3} 
= \frac{\partial \Phi}{\partial R} + \frac{1}{\rho} \frac{\partial}{\partial R} (P_\mathrm{gas} + P_\mathrm{mag}) + \frac{1}{4\pi \rho} \frac{B_\varphi^2}{R} 
= \frac{\partial \Phi}{\partial R} + \frac{1}{\rho} \frac{\partial P_\mathrm{gas}}{\partial R} + \frac{1}{8\pi \rho} \frac{\partial B_\varphi^2}{\partial R} + \frac{1}{4\pi \rho} \frac{B_\varphi^2}{R}\]

<p>å¼å¤‰å½¢ã®ãŸã‚ã«</p>

\[B_\varphi \frac{\partial}{\partial R} (R B_\varphi) 
= B_\varphi^2 + R B_\varphi \frac{\partial B_\varphi}{\partial R} 
= B_\varphi^2 + \frac{1}{2} R \frac{\partial B_\varphi^2}{\partial R} \ \Longrightarrow \ 
\frac{B_\varphi}{R} \frac{\partial}{\partial R} (R B_\varphi) 
= \frac{B_\varphi^2}{R} + \frac{1}{2} \frac{\partial B_\varphi^2}{\partial R}\]

<p>ã¨(1)å¼ã‚’ç”¨ã„ã‚‹ã¨</p>

\[\frac{\ell_z^2}{R_b^{2a}} R^{2a-3} 
= \frac{\partial \Phi}{\partial R} + \frac{1}{\rho} \frac{\partial P_\mathrm{gas}}{\partial R} + \frac{1}{4\pi \rho} \frac{B_\varphi}{R} \frac{\partial}{\partial R} (R B_\varphi) \tag{2}\]

<p>ç¶šã„ã¦\(z\)æˆåˆ†ã§ã™ã€‚\(z\)æ–¹å‘ã«ã¯ç£æ°—å¼µåŠ›ã¯åƒã‹ãªã„ãŸã‚</p>

\[0 
= \frac{\partial \Phi}{\partial z} + \frac{1}{\rho} \frac{\partial}{\partial z} (P_\mathrm{gas} + P_\mathrm{mag}) \ \Longrightarrow \ 
\frac{\partial \Phi}{\partial z} + \frac{1}{\rho} \frac{\partial P_\mathrm{gas}}{\partial z} + \frac{B_\varphi}{4\pi \rho} \frac{\partial B_\varphi}{\partial z} 
= 0 \tag{3}\]

<h3 id="ãƒˆãƒ¼ãƒ©ã‚¹ã®æ§‹é€ ">ãƒˆãƒ¼ãƒ©ã‚¹ã®æ§‹é€ </h3>

<p>ã“ã“ã§ã€åˆæœŸã®ãƒˆãƒ¼ãƒ©ã‚¹ã®æ§‹é€ ã¯ãƒãƒªãƒˆãƒ­ãƒ¼ãƒ—ã‚’ä»®å®šã—ã¾ã™ã€‚ã™ãªã‚ã¡</p>

\[P_\mathrm{gas} = K \rho^\Gamma \tag{4}\]

<p>ã®å½¢ã§ã‚ã‚‹ã¨ã—ã¾ã™ã€‚ã“ã“ã§\(K, \Gamma\)ã¯å®šæ•°ã§ã™ã€‚</p>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>ãƒãƒªãƒˆãƒ­ãƒ¼ãƒ—ã¯æ§‹é€ ã‚’ä»®å®šã™ã‚‹ã¨ãç”¨ã„ã‚‹ã“ã¨ã‚‚ã‚ã‚Œã°ã€å±€æ‰€çš„ãªçŠ¶æ…‹æ–¹ç¨‹å¼ã‚’ä»®å®šã™ã‚‹ã¨ãã«ã‚‚ç”¨ã„ã‚‹ã€ä»Šã ã«ç†è§£ã§ãã¦ã„ãªã„å¼ã§ã™...
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>ã•ã‚‰ã«å††å½¢ç£å ´ã«ã‚ˆã‚‹<a href="/mhd/alfven_wave">ã‚¢ãƒ«ãƒ´ã‚§ãƒ¼ãƒ³é€Ÿåº¦</a>ã‚’</p>

\[v_{A\varphi}^2 
= \frac{B_\varphi^2}{4\pi \rho} 
= \frac{(4\pi H)^{1/\mu}}{4\pi} (R B_\varphi)^{\frac{2(\mu-1)}{\mu}} \tag{5}\]

<p>ã®ã‚ˆã†ã«ä»®å®šã—ã¾ã™ã€‚ã“ã“ã§\(H, \mu\)ã‚‚å®šæ•°ã§ã™ã€‚ã™ã‚‹ã¨ã“ã®ä»®å®šã‹ã‚‰</p>

\[\frac{4\pi v_{A\varphi}^2}{(4\pi H)^{1/\mu}} = (R B_\varphi)^{\frac{2(\mu-1)}{\mu}} \ \Longrightarrow \ 
B_\varphi = \frac{1}{R} \left\{ \frac{4\pi v_{A\varphi}^2}{(4\pi H)^{1/\mu}}\right\}^{\frac{\mu}{2(\mu-1)}} \tag{6}\]

<p>(2), (4)å¼ã‚ˆã‚Š</p>

\[\frac{\ell_z^2}{R_b^{2a}} R^{2a-3} 
= \frac{\partial \Phi}{\partial R} + \frac{1}{\rho} \frac{\partial}{\partial R} (K \rho^\Gamma) + \frac{1}{4\pi \rho} \frac{B_\varphi}{R} \frac{\partial}{\partial R} (R B_\varphi)\]

<p>ã•ã‚‰ã«(6)å¼ã‹ã‚‰</p>

\[\begin{aligned}
&amp;\frac{\partial v_{A\varphi}^2}{\partial R} 
= \frac{(4\pi H)^{1/\mu}}{4\pi} \frac{\partial}{\partial R} (R B_\varphi)^{\frac{2(\mu-1)}{\mu}} 
= \frac{(4\pi H)^{1/\mu}}{4\pi} \frac{2(\mu-1)}{\mu} (R B_\varphi)^{\frac{2(\mu-1)}{\mu}-1} \frac{\partial}{\partial R} (R B_\varphi) 
= \frac{2(\mu-1)}{\mu} \frac{v_{A\varphi}^2}{R B_\varphi} \frac{\partial}{\partial R} (R B_\varphi) \\
&amp;\Longrightarrow \ 
\frac{\partial}{\partial R} (R B_\varphi) 
= \frac{\mu}{2(\mu-1)} \frac{R B_\varphi}{v_{A\varphi}^2} \frac{\partial v_{A\varphi}^2}{\partial R}
\end{aligned}\]

<p>ã‚ˆã‚Š</p>

\[\frac{\ell_z^2}{R_b^{2a}} R^{2a-3} 
= \frac{\partial \Phi}{\partial R} + K \Gamma \rho^{\Gamma-2} \frac{\partial \rho}{\partial R} + \frac{\mu}{2(\mu-1)} \frac{\partial v_{A\varphi}^2}{\partial R}
= \frac{\partial \Phi}{\partial R} + K \frac{\Gamma}{\Gamma-1} \frac{\partial \rho^{\Gamma-1}}{\partial R} + \frac{\mu}{2(\mu-1)} \frac{\partial v_{A\varphi}^2}{\partial R}\]

<p>ã®ã‚ˆã†ã«ãªã‚Šã¾ã™ã€‚ã“ã“ã§(4)å¼ã‹ã‚‰ã€ã‚¬ã‚¹ã®<a href="/mhd/sound_wave">éŸ³é€Ÿ</a>ã¯</p>

\[C_s^2 
= \frac{\partial P_\mathrm{gas}}{\partial \rho} 
= K \Gamma \rho^{\Gamma-1}\]

<p>ã¨ãªã‚‹ã®ã§</p>

\[-\frac{\ell_z^2}{R_b^{2a}} R^{2a-3} + \frac{\partial \Phi}{\partial R} + \frac{1}{\Gamma-1} \frac{\partial C_s^2}{\partial R} + \frac{\mu}{2(\mu-1)} \frac{\partial v_{A\varphi}^2}{\partial R} = 0\]

<p>ã®å½¢ã«ãªã‚Šã¾ã™ã€‚ã“ã®ä¸¡è¾ºã‚’\(R\)ã§ç©åˆ†ã™ã‚‹ã¨</p>

\[- \frac{1}{2a-2}\frac{\ell_z^2}{R_b^{2a}} R^{2a-2} + \Phi + \frac{C_s^2}{\Gamma-1} + \frac{\mu}{2(\mu-1)} v_{A\varphi}^2 
= (Rã«ä¾å­˜ã—ãªã„é–¢æ•°) \tag{7}\]

<p>ã‚’å¾—ã¾ã™ã€‚ç¶šã‘ã¦\(z\)æ–¹å‘ã®é‡£ã‚Šåˆã„ã®å¼(3)ã‚‚åŒæ§˜ã«å¼å¤‰å½¢ã—ã¾ã—ã‚‡ã†ã€‚å…¨ãåŒã˜å¼å¤‰å½¢ã«ã‚ˆã‚Šã€ä»¥ä¸‹ã‚’å¾—ã¾ã™ã€‚</p>

\[\frac{\partial \Phi}{\partial z} + \frac{1}{\Gamma-1} \frac{\partial C_s^2}{\partial z} + \frac{\mu}{2(\mu-1)} \frac{\partial v_{A\varphi}^2}{\partial z} = 0\]

<p>ã“ã®ä¸¡è¾ºã‚’\(z\)ã§ç©åˆ†ã™ã‚‹ã¨</p>

\[\Phi + \frac{C_s^2}{\Gamma-1} + \frac{\mu}{2(\mu-1)} v_{A\varphi}^2 
= (zã«ä¾å­˜ã—ãªã„é–¢æ•°) \tag{8}\]

<p>ã‚’å¾—ã¾ã™ã€‚</p>

<h3 id="ãƒˆãƒ¼ãƒ©ã‚¹ã®å¯†åº¦åˆ†å¸ƒã®è§£">ãƒˆãƒ¼ãƒ©ã‚¹ã®å¯†åº¦åˆ†å¸ƒã®è§£</h3>

<p>(7), (8)å¼ã‚ˆã‚Š</p>

\[- \frac{1}{2a-2} \frac{\ell_z^2}{R_b^{2a}} R^{2a-2} + (zã«ä¾å­˜ã—ãªã„é–¢æ•°) 
= (Rã«ä¾å­˜ã—ãªã„é–¢æ•°)\]

<p>å·¦è¾ºã¯\(R\)ã®ã¿ã®é–¢æ•°ãªã®ã«å¯¾ã—ã€å³è¾ºã¯\(z\)ã®ã¿ã®é–¢æ•°ã§ã™ã€‚ã‚ˆã£ã¦ã“ã‚Œã¯å®šæ•°ã®ãƒãƒ†ãƒ³ã‚·ãƒ£ãƒ«ã®å½¢ã§æ›¸ã‘ã‚‹ã“ã¨ãŒã‚ã‹ã‚Šã¾ã™ã€‚ã¤ã„ã§ã«\(\mu = \Gamma\)ã¨ã—ã¦ã—ã¾ã†ã¨</p>

\[-\frac{1}{2a-2} \frac{\ell_z^2}{R_b^{2a}} R^{2a-2} + \Phi + \frac{C_s^2}{\Gamma-1} + \frac{\Gamma}{2(\Gamma-1)} v_{A\varphi}^2 
 \equiv \Psi_b \tag{8}\]

<p>ã®ã‚ˆã†ã«æ›¸ã‘ã¾ã™ã€‚ã“ã“ã§\(\Psi_b\)ã¯å®šæ•°ã§ã™ã€‚<br />
(5)å¼ã‚ˆã‚Š</p>

\[\frac{1}{\rho} 
= (4\pi H)^{1/\Gamma} R^{\frac{2(\Gamma-1)}{\Gamma}} B_\varphi^{\frac{2(\Gamma-1)}{\Gamma}-2} 
= (4\pi H)^{1/\Gamma} R^{\frac{2(\Gamma-1)}{\Gamma}} B_\varphi^{-2/\Gamma} \ \Longrightarrow \ 
B_\varphi^2 
= 4\pi H R^{2(\Gamma-1)} \rho^\Gamma \tag{9.0}\]

<p>ã§ã™ã€‚ã“ã‚Œã‚ˆã‚Šãƒˆãƒ¼ãƒ©ã‚¹æœ€æ·±éƒ¨ã§ã®<a href="/mhd/alfven_wave">ã‚¢ãƒ«ãƒ´ã‚§ãƒ¼ãƒ³é€Ÿåº¦</a>ã¯</p>

\[v_{A\varphi}^2 
= H R^{2(\Gamma-1)} \rho^{\Gamma-1} \ \Longrightarrow \ 
v_{A\varphi, b}^2 
= H R_b^{2(\Gamma-1)} \rho_b^{\Gamma-1} \tag{9}\]

<p>ãã—ã¦ãƒˆãƒ¼ãƒ©ã‚¹æœ€æ·±éƒ¨ã§ã®<a href="/mhd/sound_wave">éŸ³é€Ÿ</a>ã‹ã‚‰ã€å®šæ•°\(K\)ã¯</p>

\[C_{s, b}^2 = \Gamma K \rho_b^{\Gamma-1} \ \Longrightarrow \ 
K 
= \frac{C_{s, b}^2}{\Gamma \rho_b^{\Gamma-1}} \tag{10}\]

<p>ã¨ãªã‚Šã¾ã™ã€‚ã•ã‚‰ã«æ–°ã—ã„ãƒ‘ãƒ©ãƒ¡ãƒ¼ã‚¿ã¨ã—ã¦ã€\(\varphi\)æ–¹å‘ç£å ´ã«ã‚ˆã‚‹ãƒˆãƒ¼ãƒ©ã‚¹æœ€æ·±éƒ¨ã§ã®ãƒ—ãƒ©ã‚ºãƒãƒ™ãƒ¼ã‚¿\(\beta_{\varphi, b}\)ã‚’å°å…¥ã™ã‚‹ã¨</p>

\[\beta_{\varphi, b} 
= \frac{P_{\mathrm{gas}, b}}{P_{\mathrm{mag}, b}} 
= \frac{K \rho_b^\Gamma}{\frac{1}{8\pi} B_{\varphi, b}^2} 
= \frac{K\rho_b^\Gamma}{\frac{1}{2} \rho_b v_{A\varphi, b}^2} 
\underbrace{=}_{(9)} \frac{K \rho_b^\Gamma}{\frac{1}{2} H R_b^{2(\Gamma-1)} \rho_b^\Gamma} \ \Longrightarrow \ 
H 
= \frac{2K}{\beta_{\varphi, b}} R_b^{-2(\Gamma-1)} \tag{11}\]

<p>ã®ã‚ˆã†ã«å®šæ•°\(H\)ãŒæ±‚ã¾ã‚Šã¾ã™ã€‚<br />
(8)å¼ã«ãŠã„ã¦ã€\(\Psi_b\)ã‚’ãƒˆãƒ¼ãƒ©ã‚¹æœ€æ·±éƒ¨\((R, z) = (R_b, z)\)ã§ã®ãƒãƒ†ãƒ³ã‚·ãƒ£ãƒ«ã®å€¤ã¨ã™ã‚‹ã¨</p>

\[\Psi_b = \Phi (R_b, 0) + \frac{C_{s, b}^2}{\Gamma-1} + \frac{\Gamma}{2(\Gamma-1)} v_{A\varphi, b}^2 - \frac{1}{2a-2} \frac{\ell_z^2}{R_b^2} 
= \Phi (R, z) + \frac{C_{s}^2}{\Gamma-1} + \frac{\Gamma}{2(\Gamma-1)} v_{A\varphi}^2 - \frac{1}{2a-2} \frac{\ell_z^2}{R_b^2} R^{2a-2}\]

<p>ã‚¬ã‚¹å¯†åº¦\(\rho(R, z)\)ã‚’æ±‚ã‚ã‚‹ãŸã‚ã«å¼å¤‰å½¢ã‚’ã—ã¾ã—ã‚‡ã†ã€‚</p>

\[\begin{aligned}
\Psi_b - \Phi(R, z) + \frac{1}{2a-2} \frac{\ell_z^2}{R_b^{2a}} R^{2a-2} 
&amp;= \frac{\overbrace{C_s^2}^{=\Gamma P_\mathrm{gas}/\rho}}{\Gamma-1} + \frac{\Gamma}{2(\Gamma-1)} \underbrace{v_{A\varphi}^2}_{(9)} 
= \frac{\Gamma}{\Gamma-1} \left( \frac{P_\mathrm{gas}}{\rho} + \frac{1}{2} H R^{2(\Gamma-1)} \rho^{\Gamma-1}\right) \\
&amp;\underbrace{=}_{(4)} \frac{\Gamma}{\Gamma-1} K \rho^{\Gamma-1} \left( 1 + \frac{H}{2K} R^{2(\Gamma-1)}\right) \\
&amp;= \frac{\Gamma}{\Gamma-1} K \rho^{\Gamma-1} \left( 1 + \frac{H}{2K} R_b^{2(\Gamma-1)} R_b^{-2(\Gamma-1)} R^{2(\Gamma-1)}\right)
\end{aligned}\]

<p>ã“ã“ã«(11)å¼ã‚’ç”¨ã„ã‚Œã°</p>

\[\Psi_b - \Phi + \frac{1}{2a-2} \frac{\ell_z^2}{R_b^{2a}} R^{2a-2} 
= \frac{\Gamma}{\Gamma-1} K \rho^{\Gamma-1} \left\{ 1 + \beta_{\varphi, b}^{-1} \left( \frac{R}{R_b} \right)^{2(\Gamma-1)} \right\}\]

<p>ã‚ˆã£ã¦ã€æ±‚ã‚ãŸã‹ã£ãŸç£æ°—æµä½“å›è»¢ãƒˆãƒ¼ãƒ©ã‚¹ã®å¯†åº¦åˆ†å¸ƒã¯</p>

\[\rho (R, z) 
= \left[ \frac{\Psi_b - \Phi(R, z) + \frac{1}{2a-2} \frac{\ell_z^2}{R_b^{2a}} R^{2a-2}}{\frac{\Gamma}{\Gamma-1} K \left\{ 1 + \beta_{\varphi, b}^{-1} \left( \frac{R}{R_b} \right)^{2(\Gamma-1)} \right\}}\right]^{\frac{1}{\Gamma-1}}\]

<p>ã®ã‚ˆã†ã«ãªã‚Šã¾ã™ã€‚å®Ÿéš›ã«ã¯\([\cdots]\)ã®ä¸­èº«ã®åˆ†å­ãŒè² ã«ãªã‚‹é ˜åŸŸãŒå­˜åœ¨ã—ã¾ã™ã€‚ã‚ˆã£ã¦ã€ã“ã®ãƒˆãƒ¼ãƒ©ã‚¹ã®ã‚¬ã‚¹åˆ†å¸ƒã¯</p>

\[\rho (R, z) 
= \left[ \frac{ \max \left( \Psi_b - \Phi(R, z) + \frac{1}{2a-2} \frac{\ell_z^2}{R_b^{2a}} R^{2a-2}, 0\right)}{\frac{\Gamma}{\Gamma-1} K \left\{ 1 + \beta_{\varphi, b}^{-1} \left( \frac{R}{R_b} \right)^{2(\Gamma-1)} \right\}}\right]^{\frac{1}{\Gamma-1}} \tag{12}\]

<p>ã®ã‚ˆã†ã«æ›¸ãã®ãŒæ­£ã—ã„ã§ã—ã‚‡ã†ã€‚</p>

<h3 id="ç£å ´ã®å¤§ãã•">ç£å ´ã®å¤§ãã•</h3>

<p>\(B_\varphi\)ã¯(9.0)å¼ã¨(11)å¼ã‚ˆã‚Š</p>

\[B_\varphi^2 
= \frac{8\pi K}{\beta_{\varphi, b}} \left( \frac{R}{R_b}\right)^{2(\Gamma-1)} \rho^\Gamma \tag{13}\]

<p>ã§ã™ã€‚ã“ã“ã§\(K\)ã¯ã€(10)å¼ã¨ç†æƒ³æ°—ä½“ã®çŠ¶æ…‹æ–¹ç¨‹å¼</p>

\[P_\mathrm{gas} 
= n k_B T 
= \frac{\rho}{\mu m_p} k_B T \ \Longrightarrow \ 
C_s^2 
= \frac{\Gamma P_\mathrm{gas}}{\rho} 
= \frac{\Gamma}{\mu m_p} k_B T \tag{14}\]

<p>ã‚’ç”¨ã„ã‚Œã°</p>

\[K = \frac{k_B }{\mu m_p} \frac{T}{\rho^{\Gamma-1}}
= \frac{k_B }{\mu m_p} \frac{T_b}{\rho_b^{\Gamma-1}} \tag{15}\]

<p>ã®ã‚ˆã†ã«ãªã‚Šã¾ã™ã€‚(15)å¼ã®æœ€å¾Œã®ç­‰å·ã¯ã€\(K\)ãŒå®šæ•°ã§ã‚ã‚‹ã“ã¨ã‹ã‚‰ãƒˆãƒ¼ãƒ©ã‚¹æœ€æ·±éƒ¨ã®å€¤ã‚’ç”¨ã„ã¦è¨˜è¿°ã§ãã‚‹ã“ã¨ã‚’ç”¨ã„ã¾ã—ãŸã€‚</p>

<p>ä»¥ä¸Šã‹ã‚‰</p>

<ul>
  <li>ãƒˆãƒ¼ãƒ©ã‚¹æœ€æ·±éƒ¨ã®ä½ç½®\(R_b\)</li>
  <li>\(L_z\)ã®\(R\)ä¾å­˜æ€§\(a\)</li>
  <li>ãƒˆãƒ¼ãƒ©ã‚¹æœ€æ·±éƒ¨ã§ã®å˜ä½ä½“ç©ã‚ãŸã‚Šã®è§’é‹å‹•é‡\(\ell_z\)</li>
  <li>ãƒˆãƒ¼ãƒ©ã‚¹æœ€æ·±éƒ¨ã§ã®ãƒ—ãƒ©ã‚ºãƒãƒ™ãƒ¼ã‚¿\(\beta_{\varphi, b}\)</li>
  <li>ãƒˆãƒ¼ãƒ©ã‚¹æœ€æ·±éƒ¨ã§ã®ã‚¬ã‚¹å¯†åº¦\(\rho_b\)</li>
  <li>ãƒˆãƒ¼ãƒ©ã‚¹æœ€æ·±éƒ¨ã§ã®æ¸©åº¦\(T_b\)</li>
  <li>ãƒãƒªãƒˆãƒ­ãƒ¼ãƒ—æŒ‡æ•°\(\Gamma=1+ \frac{1}{n}\)</li>
</ul>

<p>ã‚’ãƒ‘ãƒ©ãƒ¡ãƒ¼ã‚¿ã¨ã—ã¦äººé–“ãŒå…¥åŠ›ã™ã‚Œã°ã€ãƒˆãƒ¼ãƒ©ã‚¹ã®å¯†åº¦åˆ†å¸ƒã¨\(\varphi\)æ–¹å‘ç£å ´åˆ†å¸ƒã‚’è¨ˆç®—ã™ã‚‹ã“ã¨ãŒã§ãã¾ã™ã€‚</p>

<h2 id="ç£å ´ãªã—ãƒˆãƒ¼ãƒ©ã‚¹ã®å ´åˆ">ç£å ´ãªã—ãƒˆãƒ¼ãƒ©ã‚¹ã®å ´åˆ</h2>

<p>ç£å ´ã®ãªã„ã‚¬ã‚¹ãƒˆãƒ¼ãƒ©ã‚¹ã‚’ç”¨æ„ã—ãŸã„å ´åˆã¯ã€(12)å¼ã«ãŠã„ã¦\(\beta_{\varphi, b} \rightarrow \infty\)ã¨ã™ã‚Œã°å¾—ã‚‰ã‚Œã¾ã™ã€‚ã™ã‚‹ã¨</p>

\[\rho (R, z) 
= \left[ \frac{ \max \left( \Psi_b - \Phi(R, z) + \frac{1}{2a-2} \frac{\ell_z^2}{R_b^{2a}} R^{2a-2}, 0\right)}{\frac{\Gamma}{\Gamma-1} K}\right]^{\frac{1}{\Gamma-1}} 
\tag{16}\]

<p>ã¨ãªã‚Šã¾ã™ã€‚</p>

<h2 id="ãƒãƒ­ã‚¤ãƒ€ãƒ«ç£å ´ã‚’æŒã¤ãƒˆãƒ¼ãƒ©ã‚¹ã®å ´åˆ">ãƒãƒ­ã‚¤ãƒ€ãƒ«ç£å ´ã‚’æŒã¤ãƒˆãƒ¼ãƒ©ã‚¹ã®å ´åˆ</h2>

<p>ãƒãƒ­ã‚¤ãƒ€ãƒ«(\(R, z\)æˆåˆ†ã—ã‹æŒãŸãªã„)ç£å ´ã‚’ãƒˆãƒ¼ãƒ©ã‚¹å†…éƒ¨ã«æŒã¤ã“ã¨ã‚’è€ƒãˆã‚‹å ´åˆã€ä¸€èˆ¬ã«é‡£ã‚Šåˆã„ã®å¼ã‚’è§£ãã“ã¨ã¯å›°é›£ã§ã™ã€‚ã“ã®ãŸã‚ã€ã‚ˆãç”¨ã„ã‚‰ã‚Œã‚‹ç£å ´ã®ç”¨æ„æ‰‹æ³•ã¨ã—ã¦ã¯ã€æ¬¡ã®ã‚ˆã†ãªã‚‚ã®ãŒã‚ã‚Šã¾ã™ã€‚<br />
ç£å ´ã®ãƒ™ã‚¯ãƒˆãƒ«ãƒãƒ†ãƒ³ã‚·ãƒ£ãƒ«ã‚’\(\mathbf{A} = A_\varphi \mathbf{e}_\varphi\)ã®ã‚ˆã†ã«å®šã‚ã‚‹ã¨ã€ã“ã®ãƒ™ã‚¯ãƒˆãƒ«ãƒãƒ†ãƒ³ã‚·ãƒ£ãƒ«ã‹ã‚‰ç™ºç”Ÿã™ã‚‹ç£å ´ã¯</p>

\[\mathbf{B} 
= \nabla \times \mathbf{A} 
= -\frac{\partial A_\varphi}{\partial z} \mathbf{e}_R + \frac{1}{R} \frac{\partial}{\partial R} (R A_\varphi) \mathbf{e}_z\]

<p>ã®ã‚ˆã†ã«ãƒãƒ­ã‚¤ãƒ€ãƒ«ç£å ´ã¨ãªã‚Šã¾ã™ã€‚ã‚ˆã£ã¦ãƒ™ã‚¯ãƒˆãƒ«ãƒãƒ†ãƒ³ã‚·ãƒ£ãƒ«\(A_\varphi\)ã‚’é©å½“ã«ã€ä¾‹ãˆã°\(A_\varphi \propto \rho\)ã®ã‚ˆã†ã«å®šã‚ã¾ã™ã€‚ã‚ã‚‹ã„ã¯</p>

\[A_\varphi = A_0 \exp \left\{ - \left( \frac{R-R_b}{a} \right)^2 - \left(\frac{z}{b} \right)^2 \right\}\]

<p>ã®ã‚ˆã†ã«ã€é©å½“ãªscale height \(a, b\)ã‚’ç”¨ã„ã‚‹ã“ã¨ã§ã€ãƒˆãƒ¼ãƒ©ã‚¹ã®é™ã‚‰ã‚ŒãŸé ˜åŸŸå†…ã«ãƒãƒ­ã‚¤ãƒ€ãƒ«ç£å ´ãŒå­˜åœ¨ã™ã‚‹ã‚ˆã†ãªãƒ¢ãƒ‡ãƒ«ãŒä½œã‚Œã¾ã™ã€‚ãŸã ã—(16)å¼ã®ç£å ´ãªã—ãƒˆãƒ¼ãƒ©ã‚¹ã«ãƒãƒ­ã‚¤ãƒ€ãƒ«ç£å ´ã‚’å‹æ‰‹ã«åŠ ãˆã‚‹ã“ã¨ã§ã€åŠ›å­¦å¹³è¡¡ã‹ã‚‰ã‚ºãƒ¬ãŒç”Ÿã˜ã¾ã™ã€‚ã‚ˆã£ã¦ã“ã®ãƒãƒ­ã‚¤ãƒ€ãƒ«ç£å ´ã‚ã‚Šãƒˆãƒ¼ãƒ©ã‚¹ã¯ã€åŠ›å­¦å¹³è¡¡ãŒæˆã‚Šç«‹ã£ã¦ã„ãªã„ã“ã¨ã«æ³¨æ„ã—ã¾ã—ã‚‡ã†ã€‚<br />
ã¾ãŸã“ã®ã‚ˆã†ã«ã—ã¦åŠ ãˆã‚‰ã‚ŒãŸãƒãƒ­ã‚¤ãƒ€ãƒ«ç£å ´ã¯ã€ãã®å‘ãã«æ³¨æ„ã™ã‚‹å¿…è¦ãŒã‚ã‚Šã¾ã™ã€‚ã‚‚ã—ãƒ–ãƒ©ãƒƒã‚¯ãƒ›ãƒ¼ãƒ«é™ç€å††ç›¤ã®ã‚ˆã†ãªç³»ã®ã‚·ãƒŸãƒ¥ãƒ¬ãƒ¼ã‚·ãƒ§ãƒ³åˆæœŸæ¡ä»¶ã¨ã—ã¦ç”¨ã„ã‚‹å ´åˆã€ã“ã®ãƒ™ã‚¯ãƒˆãƒ«ãƒãƒ†ãƒ³ã‚·ãƒ£ãƒ«\(A_\varphi\)ã¯é™ç€å††ç›¤ä¸­ã‚’æµã‚Œã‚‹é›»æµã«ã‚ˆã£ã¦ä½œã‚‰ã‚Œã‚‹ã¨è€ƒãˆã‚‹ã“ã¨ãŒã§ãã¾ã™ã€‚ã™ã‚‹ã¨ä¸‹å›³ã®ã‚ˆã†ã«ã€ãã®é›»æµã‹ã‚‰å³ã­ã˜ã®æ³•å‰‡ãŒæˆã‚Šç«‹ã¤ã‚ˆã†ã«ç£å ´ã®å‘ã(ã“ã“ã§ã¯ãƒ™ã‚¯ãƒˆãƒ«ãƒãƒ†ãƒ³ã‚·ãƒ£ãƒ«ã®ç¬¦å·)ã‚’å®šã‚ãªã‘ã‚Œã°ãªã‚Šã¾ã›ã‚“ã€‚</p>

<p><img src="/assets/images/compact/torus_001.png" alt="" /></p>

<h2 id="ãƒˆãƒ¼ãƒ©ã‚¹ã®å‘¨å›²ã«ã¤ã„ã¦">ãƒˆãƒ¼ãƒ©ã‚¹ã®å‘¨å›²ã«ã¤ã„ã¦</h2>

<p>å…ˆè¿°ã®é€šã‚Šã€(12)å¼ã‚„(16)å¼ã§è¡¨ã•ã‚Œã‚‹ã‚ˆã†ãªãƒˆãƒ¼ãƒ©ã‚¹ã§ã¯ã€ã‚¬ã‚¹å¯†åº¦ãŒ0ã«ãªã‚‹é ˜åŸŸãŒå­˜åœ¨ã—ã¾ã™ã€‚ã—ã‹ã—(ç£æ°—)æµä½“ã‚·ãƒŸãƒ¥ãƒ¬ãƒ¼ã‚·ãƒ§ãƒ³ãªã©ã‚’è¡Œã†å ´åˆã€\(\rho = 0\)ã§ã¯<a href="/mhd/sound_wave">éŸ³é€Ÿ</a>\(C_s^2 = \frac{\gamma P_\mathrm{gas}}{\rho}\)ã‚„<a href="/mhd/alfven_wave">ã‚¢ãƒ«ãƒ´ã‚§ãƒ¼ãƒ³é€Ÿåº¦</a>\(v_A = \frac{B}{\sqrt{4\pi \rho}}\)ãŒç„¡é™å¤§ã¨ãªã‚Šã€è¨ˆç®—ãŒä¸å¯èƒ½ã¨ãªã‚Šã¾ã™ã€‚<br />
ãã“ã§é™ç€å††ç›¤ãªã©ã®ã‚·ãƒŸãƒ¥ãƒ¬ãƒ¼ã‚·ãƒ§ãƒ³ã§ã¯ã€ãƒˆãƒ¼ãƒ©ã‚¹ã®å‘¨å›²ã«é™æ°´åœ§å¹³è¡¡ãªå®šæ¸©ã‚³ãƒ­ãƒŠ(ãƒãƒ­ãƒ¼)ã‚’é…ç½®ã—ã¾ã™ã€‚\(R\)æ–¹å‘ã®é‡£ã‚Šåˆã„ã®å¼ã‚ˆã‚Š</p>

\[0 = - \frac{\partial \Phi}{\partial R} - \frac{1}{\rho_c} \frac{\partial \rho_c}{\partial R}\]

<p>ã“ã“ã«ç†æƒ³æ°—ä½“ã®çŠ¶æ…‹æ–¹ç¨‹å¼(14)å¼ã‚’ç”¨ã„ã¾ã™ã€‚ã“ã®ã¨ãã€ã“ã®ã‚³ãƒ­ãƒŠæˆåˆ†ã¯æ¸©åº¦ãŒä¸€å®šã§ã‚ã‚‹ã“ã¨ã‚’ç”¨ã„ã‚‹ã¨ã€ä¸Šã®é‡£ã‚Šåˆã„ã®å¼ã¯\(R\)ã§ç©åˆ†ã™ã‚‹ã“ã¨ãŒã§ãã¦</p>

\[C = - \Phi - \frac{k_B T}{\mu m_p} \ln \rho_c\]

<p>ã¨ãªã‚Šã¾ã™ã€‚å·¦è¾ºã®\(C\)ã¯ç©åˆ†å®šæ•°ã§ã™ã€‚ä»¥ä¸Šã‹ã‚‰</p>

\[\rho_c 
= \exp\left\{ \frac{\mu m_p}{k_B T} (-\Phi -C)\right\} 
= \rho_{c, 0} \exp \left\{ - \frac{\mu m_p}{k_B T} (\Phi - \Phi_b)\right\} \tag{17}\]

<p>ã¨ãªã‚Šã¾ã™ã€‚ã“ã“ã§\(\Phi_b = \Phi(R_b, 0)\)ã§ã™ã€‚ç©åˆ†å®šæ•°ã‚’ã“ã®ã‚ˆã†ã«å®šã‚ã¦ãŠã‘ã°ã€ãƒˆãƒ¼ãƒ©ã‚¹ã®æœ€æ·±éƒ¨\((R_b, 0)\)ã§ã®ã‚³ãƒ­ãƒŠæˆåˆ†ã®ã‚¬ã‚¹å¯†åº¦ãŒ\(\rho_{c, 0}\)ã§ã‚ã‚‹ã¨ä¸€çœ¼ã§åˆ¤æ–­ã™ã‚‹ã“ã¨ãŒã§ãã¦ä¾¿åˆ©ã§ã™ã€‚</p>

<h2 id="ãªãœå¹³è¡¡çŠ¶æ…‹ã«ã“ã ã‚ã‚‹ã®ã‹">ãªãœã€Œå¹³è¡¡çŠ¶æ…‹ã€ã«ã“ã ã‚ã‚‹ã®ã‹ï¼Ÿ</h2>

<p>ä¾‹ãˆã°ã€ãƒˆãƒ¼ãƒ©ã‚¹ã®ä¸­ã«ã‚ã‚‹å¼±ç£å ´ã«ã‚ˆã£ã¦ç™ºç”Ÿã™ã‚‹<a href="/mhd/mri">ç£æ°—å›è»¢ä¸å®‰å®šæ€§</a>ã‚’æ•°å€¤è¨ˆç®—ã‹ã‚‰æ˜ã‚‰ã‹ã«ã—ãŸã„ã¨è€ƒãˆãŸã¨ã—ã¾ã™ã€‚</p>

<h2 id="ãƒˆãƒ¼ãƒ©ã‚¹ã®å¯è¦–åŒ–">ãƒˆãƒ¼ãƒ©ã‚¹ã®å¯è¦–åŒ–</h2>

<p>å®Ÿéš›ã«<a href="https://julialang.org/">Juliaè¨€èª</a>ã‚’ç”¨ã„ã¦ãƒˆãƒ¼ãƒ©ã‚¹ã®ã‚¬ã‚¹å¯†åº¦åˆ†å¸ƒãªã©ã‚’è¨ˆç®—ã—ã€ãã‚Œã‚’ã‚«ãƒ©ãƒ¼ã‚³ãƒ³ãƒˆã‚¢ã¨ã—ã¦å¯è¦–åŒ–ã™ã‚‹ã‚½ãƒ¼ã‚¹ã‚³ãƒ¼ãƒ‰ã‚’ä»¥ä¸‹ã«ç¤ºã—ã¾ã™ã€‚
ã“ã“ã§ã¯ãƒˆãƒ¼ãƒ©ã‚¹å†…ã«ã¯æ–¹ä½è§’ç£å ´\(B_\varphi\)ãŒå­˜åœ¨ã™ã‚‹ã¨ã—ãŸ(12)å¼ã‚’ç”¨ã„ã¾ã—ãŸã€‚è¨ˆç®—ã«éš›ã—ã¦ã€æ–¹ç¨‹å¼ã¯å…¨ã¦è¦æ ¼åŒ–ã•ã‚Œã¦ã„ã‚‹ã‚‚ã®ã¨ã—ã¦ã€ç‰©ç†å®šæ•°\(G, \mu, m_p, k_B\)ã¯å…¨ã¦1ã¨ã—ã¦ã„ã¾ã™ã€‚ã¾ãŸã“ã®ã¨ããƒˆãƒ¼ãƒ©ã‚¹ã®ãƒ‘ãƒ©ãƒ¡ãƒ¼ã‚¿ã¯ãã‚Œãã‚Œ\(R_b = 5, a = 0, T_b = 0.01, \rho_b = 1, \Gamma = 4/3, \beta_b = 100\)ãªã©ã§ã™ã€‚ã•ã‚‰ã«ã“ã®ãƒˆãƒ¼ãƒ©ã‚¹ã‚’å½¢æˆã™ã‚‹é‡åŠ›ãƒãƒ†ãƒ³ã‚·ãƒ£ãƒ«ã¯</p>

\[\Phi(R, z) 
= - \frac{GM}{\sqrt{R^2 + z^2} - r_g}\]

<p>ã®ã‚ˆã†ã«æ“¬ãƒ‹ãƒ¥ãƒ¼ãƒˆãƒ³ãƒãƒ†ãƒ³ã‚·ãƒ£ãƒ«ã§ä¸ãˆã‚‰ã‚Œã‚‹ã¨ã—ã¾ã™ã€‚ã•ã‚‰ã«ãƒˆãƒ¼ãƒ©ã‚¹ä¸­å¿ƒã®è§’é‹å‹•é‡\(\ell_z\)ã¯ã€(ã‚¬ã‚¹åœ§å‹¾é…ã«ã‚ˆã‚‹åŠ›ã‚’ç„¡è¦–ã—ãŸ)ãƒ‹ãƒ¥ãƒ¼ãƒˆãƒ³ãƒãƒ†ãƒ³ã‚·ãƒ£ãƒ«ã¨é å¿ƒåŠ›ã®é‡£ã‚Šåˆã„ã‹ã‚‰</p>

\[\frac{\ell_z^2}{R_b^3} = \frac{GM}{R_b^2} \ \Longrightarrow \ 
\ell_z = \sqrt{GM R_b}\]

<p>ã¨å®šã‚ã¾ã—ãŸã€‚ã•ã‚‰ã«ãƒãƒ­ãƒ¼ã®ãƒ‘ãƒ©ãƒ¡ãƒ¼ã‚¿ã¯\(\rho_{c, 0} = 10^{-4}, T_c = 5\)ã¨ã—ã¦ã„ã¾ã™ã€‚</p>

<div class="language-julia highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="k">using</span> <span class="n">Plots</span>
<span class="n">gr</span><span class="x">()</span>

<span class="c"># compute gravitational potential Phi</span>
<span class="k">function</span><span class="nf"> Phi</span><span class="x">(</span><span class="n">M</span><span class="x">,</span> <span class="n">Rz</span><span class="x">)</span>
    <span class="n">R</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">Rz</span><span class="x">[</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="x">]</span>
    <span class="n">z</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">Rz</span><span class="x">[</span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="x">]</span>
    <span class="n">r</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">sqrt</span><span class="x">(</span><span class="n">R</span> <span class="o">^</span> <span class="mi">2</span> <span class="o">+</span> <span class="n">z</span> <span class="o">^</span> <span class="mi">2</span><span class="x">)</span>
    <span class="n">rg</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="mf">0.01</span>
    <span class="k">if</span> <span class="n">r</span> <span class="o">&lt;=</span> <span class="n">rg</span>
        <span class="n">Phi</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="o">-</span> <span class="n">prevfloat</span><span class="x">(</span><span class="n">typemax</span><span class="x">(</span><span class="kt">Float64</span><span class="x">))</span>
    <span class="k">else</span>
        <span class="n">Phi</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="o">-</span> <span class="n">M</span> <span class="o">/</span> <span class="x">(</span><span class="n">r</span><span class="o">-</span><span class="n">rg</span><span class="x">)</span>
    <span class="k">end</span>
    <span class="k">return</span> <span class="n">Phi</span>
<span class="k">end</span>

<span class="c"># compute effective Psib (= Psi @ (Rb, 0))</span>
<span class="k">function</span><span class="nf"> Psib</span><span class="x">(</span><span class="n">inputs</span><span class="x">)</span>
    <span class="c"># decode from arguments</span>
    <span class="n">Gamma</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">inputs</span><span class="x">[</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="x">]</span>
    <span class="n">Tb</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">inputs</span><span class="x">[</span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="x">]</span>
    <span class="n">rhob</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">inputs</span><span class="x">[</span><span class="mi">3</span><span class="x">]</span>
    <span class="n">Rb</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">inputs</span><span class="x">[</span><span class="mi">4</span><span class="x">]</span>
    <span class="n">betab</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">inputs</span><span class="x">[</span><span class="mi">5</span><span class="x">]</span>
    <span class="n">M</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">inputs</span><span class="x">[</span><span class="mi">6</span><span class="x">]</span>
    <span class="c"># compute effective potential Psib</span>
    <span class="n">Gamma1</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">Gamma</span> <span class="o">-</span> <span class="mi">1</span>
    <span class="n">K</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">Tb</span> <span class="o">/</span> <span class="n">rhob</span> <span class="o">^</span> <span class="n">Gamma1</span>
    <span class="n">Csb2</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">Gamma</span> <span class="o">*</span> <span class="n">K</span> <span class="o">*</span> <span class="n">rhob</span> <span class="o">^</span> <span class="n">Gamma1</span>
    <span class="n">H</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="mi">2</span> <span class="o">*</span> <span class="n">K</span> <span class="o">/</span> <span class="x">(</span><span class="n">betab</span><span class="o">*</span><span class="n">Rb</span><span class="o">^</span><span class="x">(</span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="o">*</span><span class="n">Gamma1</span><span class="x">))</span>
    <span class="n">vab2</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">H</span> <span class="o">*</span> <span class="n">Rb</span> <span class="o">^</span> <span class="x">(</span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="o">*</span><span class="n">Gamma1</span><span class="x">)</span> <span class="o">*</span> <span class="n">rhob</span> <span class="o">^</span> <span class="n">Gamma1</span>
    <span class="n">first</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="o">-</span> <span class="n">lz</span> <span class="o">^</span> <span class="mi">2</span> <span class="o">/</span> <span class="x">((</span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="o">*</span><span class="n">a</span><span class="o">-</span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="x">)</span><span class="o">*</span><span class="n">Rb</span><span class="o">^</span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="x">)</span>
    <span class="n">second</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">Phi</span><span class="x">(</span><span class="n">M</span><span class="x">,</span> <span class="x">[</span><span class="n">Rb</span><span class="x">,</span> <span class="mi">0</span><span class="x">])</span>
    <span class="n">third</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">Csb2</span> <span class="o">/</span> <span class="n">Gamma1</span>
    <span class="n">forth</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">Gamma</span> <span class="o">/</span> <span class="x">(</span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="o">*</span><span class="n">Gamma1</span><span class="x">)</span> <span class="o">*</span> <span class="n">vab2</span>
    <span class="k">return</span> <span class="n">first</span> <span class="o">+</span> <span class="n">second</span> <span class="o">+</span> <span class="n">third</span> <span class="o">+</span> <span class="n">forth</span>
<span class="k">end</span>

<span class="c"># set input parameters for torus</span>
<span class="n">Rb</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="mi">5</span>
<span class="n">a</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="mi">0</span>
<span class="n">Tb</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="mf">0.01</span>
<span class="n">rhob</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="mi">1</span>
<span class="n">Gamma</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="mi">1</span> <span class="o">+</span> <span class="mi">1</span> <span class="o">/</span> <span class="mi">3</span>
<span class="n">betab</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="mi">10</span> <span class="o">^</span> <span class="mi">2</span>
<span class="n">M</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="mi">1</span>
<span class="n">lz</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">sqrt</span><span class="x">(</span><span class="n">M</span> <span class="o">*</span> <span class="n">Rb</span><span class="x">)</span>
<span class="c"># set input parameter for corona</span>
<span class="n">Tc</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="mi">5</span>
<span class="n">rhoc0</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="mi">10</span> <span class="o">^</span> <span class="x">(</span><span class="o">-</span><span class="mi">4</span><span class="x">)</span>
<span class="c"># set the number of grids</span>
<span class="n">nR</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="mi">100</span>
<span class="n">nz</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="mi">200</span>
<span class="c"># set (R, z) cylindrical coordinates</span>
<span class="n">Rmin</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="mf">0.01</span>
<span class="n">Rmax</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="mf">15.01</span>
<span class="n">zmin</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="o">-</span><span class="mf">7.5</span>
<span class="n">zmax</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="mf">7.5</span>
<span class="n">Rs</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">range</span><span class="x">(</span><span class="n">Rmin</span><span class="x">,</span> <span class="n">Rmax</span><span class="x">,</span> <span class="n">length</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="n">nR</span><span class="x">)</span>
<span class="n">zs</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">range</span><span class="x">(</span><span class="n">zmin</span><span class="x">,</span> <span class="n">zmax</span><span class="x">,</span> <span class="n">length</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="n">nz</span><span class="x">)</span>
<span class="c"># encode to torus inputs</span>
<span class="n">inputs</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="x">[</span><span class="n">Gamma</span><span class="x">,</span> <span class="n">Tb</span><span class="x">,</span> <span class="n">rhob</span><span class="x">,</span> <span class="n">Rb</span><span class="x">,</span> <span class="n">betab</span><span class="x">,</span> <span class="n">M</span><span class="x">]</span>
<span class="n">Gamma1</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">Gamma</span> <span class="o">-</span> <span class="mi">1</span>
<span class="n">K</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">Tb</span> <span class="o">/</span> <span class="n">rhob</span> <span class="o">^</span> <span class="n">Gamma1</span>
<span class="c">###### main loop #####</span>
<span class="n">rhos</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="x">[]</span>
<span class="n">emags</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="x">[]</span>
<span class="k">for</span> <span class="n">z</span> <span class="k">in</span> <span class="n">zs</span>
    <span class="k">for</span> <span class="n">R</span> <span class="k">in</span> <span class="n">Rs</span>
        <span class="c"># compute density</span>
        <span class="n">nume</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">Psib</span><span class="x">(</span><span class="n">inputs</span><span class="x">)</span> <span class="o">-</span> <span class="n">Phi</span><span class="x">(</span><span class="n">M</span><span class="x">,</span> <span class="x">[</span><span class="n">R</span><span class="x">,</span> <span class="n">z</span><span class="x">])</span> <span class="o">+</span> <span class="n">lz</span> <span class="o">^</span> <span class="mi">2</span> <span class="o">*</span> <span class="n">R</span> <span class="o">^</span> <span class="x">(</span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="o">*</span><span class="n">a</span><span class="o">-</span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="x">)</span> <span class="o">/</span> <span class="x">((</span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="o">*</span><span class="n">a</span><span class="o">-</span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="x">)</span><span class="o">*</span><span class="n">Rb</span><span class="o">^</span><span class="x">(</span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="o">*</span><span class="n">a</span><span class="x">))</span>
        <span class="n">deno</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">Gamma</span> <span class="o">*</span> <span class="n">K</span> <span class="o">*</span> <span class="x">(</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="o">+</span><span class="x">(</span><span class="n">R</span><span class="o">/</span><span class="n">Rb</span><span class="x">)</span><span class="o">^</span><span class="x">(</span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="o">*</span><span class="n">Gamma1</span><span class="x">)</span><span class="o">/</span><span class="n">betab</span><span class="x">)</span> <span class="o">/</span> <span class="n">Gamma1</span>
        <span class="n">rho</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="x">(</span><span class="n">max</span><span class="x">(</span><span class="n">nume</span><span class="x">,</span> <span class="mi">0</span><span class="x">)</span><span class="o">/</span><span class="n">deno</span><span class="x">)</span> <span class="o">^</span> <span class="x">(</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="o">/</span><span class="n">Gamma1</span><span class="x">)</span>
        <span class="c"># add hydrostatic equilibrium compotent</span>
        <span class="n">rhoc</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">rhoc0</span> <span class="o">*</span> <span class="n">exp</span><span class="x">(</span><span class="o">-</span><span class="x">(</span><span class="n">Phi</span><span class="x">(</span><span class="n">M</span><span class="x">,</span> <span class="x">[</span><span class="n">R</span><span class="x">,</span> <span class="n">z</span><span class="x">])</span><span class="o">-</span><span class="n">Phi</span><span class="x">(</span><span class="n">M</span><span class="x">,</span> <span class="x">[</span><span class="n">Rb</span><span class="x">,</span> <span class="mi">0</span><span class="x">]))</span><span class="o">/</span><span class="n">Tc</span><span class="x">)</span>
        <span class="n">append!</span><span class="x">(</span><span class="n">rhos</span><span class="x">,</span> <span class="n">log10</span><span class="x">(</span><span class="n">rho</span><span class="o">+</span><span class="n">rhoc</span><span class="x">))</span>
        <span class="c"># compute magnetic energy</span>
        <span class="n">emag</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">K</span> <span class="o">*</span> <span class="n">rho</span> <span class="o">^</span> <span class="n">Gamma</span> <span class="o">/</span> <span class="n">betab</span> <span class="o">*</span> <span class="x">(</span><span class="n">R</span><span class="o">/</span><span class="n">Rb</span><span class="x">)</span> <span class="o">^</span> <span class="x">(</span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="o">*</span><span class="n">Gamma1</span><span class="x">)</span>
        <span class="n">append!</span><span class="x">(</span><span class="n">emags</span><span class="x">,</span> <span class="n">log10</span><span class="x">(</span><span class="n">emag</span><span class="x">))</span>
    <span class="k">end</span>
<span class="k">end</span>
<span class="c">##### main loop end #####</span>
<span class="c"># make density contour</span>
<span class="n">contour</span><span class="x">(</span><span class="n">Rs</span><span class="x">,</span> <span class="n">zs</span><span class="x">,</span> <span class="n">rhos</span><span class="x">,</span> <span class="n">fill</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="nb">true</span><span class="x">,</span> <span class="n">linewidth</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="x">,</span> <span class="n">levels</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="mi">20</span><span class="x">,</span>  
        <span class="n">aspect_ratio</span><span class="o">=:</span><span class="n">equal</span><span class="x">,</span> <span class="n">xlim</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="x">[</span><span class="n">Rmin</span><span class="x">,</span> <span class="n">Rmax</span><span class="x">],</span> <span class="n">ylim</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="x">[</span><span class="n">zmin</span><span class="x">,</span> <span class="n">zmax</span><span class="x">],</span> <span class="n">xlabel</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="s">"R"</span><span class="x">,</span> <span class="n">ylabel</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="s">"z"</span><span class="x">,</span> <span class="n">title</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="s">"Log(Density)"</span><span class="x">,</span> <span class="n">extend</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="s">"both"</span><span class="x">)</span>
<span class="n">savefig</span><span class="x">(</span><span class="s">"density.png"</span><span class="x">)</span>
<span class="c"># make magnetic energy contour</span>
<span class="n">contour</span><span class="x">(</span><span class="n">Rs</span><span class="x">,</span> <span class="n">zs</span><span class="x">,</span> <span class="n">emags</span><span class="x">,</span> <span class="n">c</span><span class="o">=:</span><span class="n">ice</span><span class="x">,</span> <span class="n">fill</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="nb">true</span><span class="x">,</span> <span class="n">linewidth</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="x">,</span> <span class="n">levels</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="mi">20</span><span class="x">,</span>  
        <span class="n">aspect_ratio</span><span class="o">=:</span><span class="n">equal</span><span class="x">,</span> <span class="n">xlim</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="x">[</span><span class="n">Rmin</span><span class="x">,</span> <span class="n">Rmax</span><span class="x">],</span> <span class="n">ylim</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="x">[</span><span class="n">zmin</span><span class="x">,</span> <span class="n">zmax</span><span class="x">],</span> <span class="n">xlabel</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="s">"R"</span><span class="x">,</span> <span class="n">ylabel</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="s">"z"</span><span class="x">,</span> <span class="n">title</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="s">"Log(Magnetic Energy)"</span><span class="x">)</span>
<span class="n">savefig</span><span class="x">(</span><span class="s">"magnetic_energy.png"</span><span class="x">)</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

